dct_description_sm: California as an island with indented northern coast.

Issued in: A new systeme of the mathematicks containing ... a new geography or a discription of the most eminent countries and coasts of the World / Jonas Moore. -- Printed for Robert Scott, London, 1681.
Includes French and English place names.
Probably copied from Duval's map of 1661.
